Explanation:

The problem requires finding if the first player can force a win in the modified game. We iterate from 1 to the maximum choosable integer (maxChoosableInteger) and add each number to the total. If the total becomes greater than or equal to the desiredTotal, the first player can force a win. Otherwise, the first player cannot force a win.

